      Server component. Renders: eyebrow `HERO_B_EYEBROW`; an `<h1>` composed as
      `{HERO_B_LINE_1}<span class="text-[color:var(--color-accent)]">
      {HERO_B_LINE_2}</span>{HERO_B_LINE_3}` (the word `brain` is wrapped in an
      inline accent span per JSX line 38 — this corrects the prior plan's
      assumption of a flat single-line string); below, the two dim subhead
      lines from `HERO_B_SUBHEAD_LINES` separated by a `<br/>`.
- [x] Create `cookbook-blocks/Step/index.tsx`. Maps to JSX `<Step/>` (lines
      234–244). Props: `{ n: string, what: string, children: ReactNode }`.
      Renders a 40px / 1fr grid: accent `step {n}` label on the left, then
      bold `{what}` title + `children` body on the right. Server component.
- [x] Create `cookbook-blocks/RecipeWorked/index.tsx`. Maps to JSX
      `<RecipeWorked/>` (lines 246–268). Props: `{ tools: string, slot:
      string, wiring: string, seeding: string }`. Renders, in vertical order:
      `MCP TOOLS EXPOSED` eyebrow + accent `tools` line; `UNWIRED SLOT(S)`
      eyebrow + foreground `slot` block (in a card with monospace font); a
