      paragraph wrapper, `<Bullet/>` row (accent `·` glyph + body), `<C/>`
      inline code span (matches JSX lines 220–233 — colocate these as small
      named exports inside `cookbook-blocks/textHelpers.tsx` or as top-level
      consts inside RecipeBody — implementor's call, but quote the JSX shape).
      State: NONE (recipeKey is a prop). Note the additional code samples
      (`ORIENT_GOOD_SAMPLE`, `CONFIG_SKELETON_SAMPLE`) extend
      `_data/codeSamples.ts` from step 1 — implementor adds them when
      authoring this step.
- [x] Create `Cookbook/RecipeRail/index.tsx`. Top of file: `'use client'`.
